Routes

GET     /user/:id                     |     Fetch user information (including scores)
POST    /user/:id                     |     Modify user information (including scores)
  => if / else to check what to update

DELETE  /user/:id                     |     Delete user
GET     /user/login                   |     Log user
POST    /user/signup                  |     Register user (+send email?)
GET     /user/recover-password        |     Send recover password email

User = {
  username,
  email,
  password,
  salt / hash,
  avatar (string),
}

Scores = {
  userId,
  score,
  won (boolean),
}

=> Total score, number of parties played, number of parties won, success rate